This paper is about unsupervised neural machine translation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes adversarial training methods, which is a common technique in machine learning and falls under the category of deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of image captioning, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper uses optimization techniques to improve the performance of the model, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
